Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Ghin. Let him eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat Ball of Doom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're damn annoying!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell you to prepare food,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all you have to do is\Nobediently follow orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's probably enough\Nfor 100 meals in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.64,0:02:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to your ship right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Owner Zeff!\N--Owner Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z... Zeff?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Protect Baratie!\NThe Great Pirate, Red Foot Zeff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NWhat're you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we revive even those on the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our restaurant will be\Ncompletely taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they have the will to fight, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, defeated warrior\Nof the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C... Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg is a defeated warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then even the ruler of\Nthe East Blue couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the pirate fleet with\N50 ships couldn't sail across...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... You must be Red Foot Zeff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An incomparable pirate who was\Na cook and yet also a captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I live as a cook now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it that way, it sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though rather than living as a cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like you can live only as a cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Foot Zeff was a master of kicks\Nwho never used his hands in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that his strong\Nlegs crushed bedrock
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even left footprints on steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Red Foot referred to your shoes,\Nwhich were covered in the blood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:05:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that spattered as you\Nkicked your enemies down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you no longer have\Nthat precious leg of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unlucky for you to\Nhave an accident at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, losing one of your legs\Nmust mean you are unable to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cook without a leg\Nas long as I have these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to say?\NJust come right out and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Foot Zeff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man who once entered\Nthe Grand Line and came back unhurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a\Nlogbook with the full year of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your journey chronicled in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You've been to\Nthe Grand Line, too, pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My logbook, huh?\NIndeed, I have it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The logbook is the pride of all\Nthe crewmen that I traveled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too important to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll just take it from you by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I fell from the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, I'm still\NDon Krieg, the strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's merely a dark sea route.\NTo sail across it, I had enough power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and forces... as well as ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that was regrettable\Nwas that I lacked information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't know things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your logbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll form a large pirate fleet\Nagain and seize the One Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll stand on top\Nin this Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, back off, chore boy!\NYou're no match for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't back off on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let it pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to. I just stated a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\NI'll conquer the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we didn't\Nhave information,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a fleet with 5,000 men was\Nwiped out in just seven days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a devilish sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way someone\Nlike you can sail across it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seven days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Krieg's pirate ships were\Nwiped out in just seven days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't find\Nthose kinds of jokes funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to let it drop,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then how about I just crush you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead if you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, I'll send\Nyou to the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna fight, Luffy? Need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you don't need help,\Nthough, th-that's fine too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Usopp! You stopped by?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Just watch from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah? T-Too bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you say so, what can we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But if push comes\Nto shove, we'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-So, g-g-good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for, Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your crewmembers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a small group you got!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?!\NI've got two more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You counted me, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go feed my underlings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who don't want to die can\Nabandon the restaurant and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm after are the\Nlogbook and this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you still wish\Nto be uselessly killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's a bother, but I'll\Nbury you into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:10:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Zoro went in there.\NIt should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Are they really okay, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Big Sis Nami, should we go in, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Big Sis?!\N--Ahhh! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Sis Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Ahh, what is it?\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sanji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something you\Nshould apologize for, underling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each cook at this restaurant acted\Nas they felt was right. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner! Why are you acting as\Nif you're taking Sanji's side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! He's responsible\Nfor this whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to put your precious\Nrestaurant out of business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you felt what it's like to\Nbe on the brink of starvation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing food and water\Non this grand ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how scary it is?!\NDo you know how hard it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What do you mean, Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference between Sanji and you all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is whether you know it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying that Sanji knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to grumble,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave the restaurant from\Nthe back door already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear it if I was just\Nbeaten and didn't fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay, too! This is the\Nrestaurant where I work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have anywhere\Nelse to go anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!\NYou saw how powerful Don is, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding someone who's\Nhungry is my morality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those we'll be dealing with\Nare plunderers with full bellies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you complain even\Nwhen I beat up your fellow pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone's going to\Ntake over this restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's you, I'll kill\Nthem without hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Letting him live and now\Nkilling him? You're hopeless, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you damn cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see? He's kinda cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better get out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Even if it's Krieg,\Nhe's a wreck with injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! You said you didn't know\Nanything about the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you've been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still true that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened on the seventh day\Nafter we entered the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it\Nwas a dream or reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't been able\Nto come to terms with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still just can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the 50-ship fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was wiped out by only one man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as this man appeared,\Nhe sank the ships one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we hadn't been lucky enough\Nto have that storm then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our main ship would've been\Ncompletely destroyed as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how many\Nships we have left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just so dreadful that I\Ndon't want to accept it as reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that man's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sharp, hawk-like eyes whose glare\Nalone gives one the chill of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...must be Hawk-Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.96,0:15:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you felt his eyes were like\Na hawk's isn't proof in and of itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what this man did is\Nenough proof that it's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You know him, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He's the man I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went out to sea to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it possible that that man had\Nsome deep grudge towards you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never did anything to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you guys disturbed\Nhis nap or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be damned if he crushed\Nour fleet for such a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so worked up.\NIt's just an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just giving an example of what\Nkind of place the Grand Line is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck kind of place is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably means that\Nanything can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy! Let's not\Ngo to a place like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:17:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It sounds so exciting!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it should be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get the concept of\N"danger" into your thick skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my goal is now completely\Nnarrowed down to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man... I can see\Nthat man if I go there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like you die before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you didn't\Nhave to call us "stupid."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I decided to become\Nthe strongest swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to devote my life to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it was my decision, the only\None who can call me stupid is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! That's just natural\Nas a man of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.95,0:18:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you idiots understand\Nthe current situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship moored in front\Nof the restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the huge Galleon that\Nbelongs to Don Krieg,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commodore of the "pirate fleet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna escape from reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do it after surviving\Nthis life-or-death crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're saved!!\N--We're saved!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! We're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free from that nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came back alive from\Nthe pirate graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which means that we can now\Nhead to the Grand Line again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are we going to that place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more objections, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, abandon this wrecked ship\Nthat could sink at any moment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take over the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our enemy's just some punk cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you take your opponent lightly,\Nthat's still more than enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!\NWe can hear their war cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:20:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect the ship to\Nthe end! It's our restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of our way, cooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main ship was... cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut?! It was cut, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This huge Galleon was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the anchor! Or we'll be\Nswallowed along with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.34,0:21:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Nami, Yosaku and Johnny\Nare still on our ship out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It might be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosaku! Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the ship?! It's gone!\NWhat happened to Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That... I'm sorry, Big Bro. She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya! Tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that if we're linked\Nby fate, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She took all the treasure and ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What'd you say?!\N--Wh-What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That son of a bitch!\NHe followed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man I've been looking for. I never\Nthought I'd be able to see him this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.31,0:24:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you gonna fight him?\N--Yeah. I went out to sea to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Zoro, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I this far from\Nthe world's strongest?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the world's strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.99,0:24:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro!!\N--Zoro!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.66,0:24:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.99,0:24:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hawk-Eye Mihawk! The Great\NSwordsman Zoro Falls on the Sea"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
